{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/CSS占位图片/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Orainsink's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"611e1cca-0320-5aa3-8eaf-3ac69e43ef1d","excerpt":"较大图片加载时,为了用户体验,在图片完全加载前需要一个占位的背景图片. 更高级一点的是类似微博知乎那种占位. 不过这里只写出一种较为简单的实现方式. 通过伪类,设置img的背景为本地图片,至于位置或者大小,视情况自己填","tableOfContents":"","html":"<p>较大图片加载时,为了用户体验,在图片完全加载前需要一个占位的背景图片.</p>\n<p>更高级一点的是类似微博知乎那种占位.</p>\n<p>不过这里只写出一种较为简单的实现方式.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">img::after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'xxxx.png'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>通过伪类,设置img的背景为本地图片,至于位置或者大小,视情况自己填</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS占位图片","date":"2019/05/13","description":null,"tags":["前端","css"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/CSS占位图片/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/SPA页面的SSR优化/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Vue的SSR优化"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/CSS-三栏布局中间自适应/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS-三栏布局中间自适应"}}}}}